<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rules and Regulations</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css"> <!-- Link to your external CSS file -->
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .main {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #333;
        }
        ul.rules {
            list-style: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        ul.rules li {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="main">
            <h1>Rules and Regulations</h1>
            <ul class="rules">
                <li>Students must carry their college ID card at all times while using the bus service.</li>
                <li>Eating and drinking are not allowed on the bus.</li>
                <li>Students must be at the bus stop at least 10 minutes before the scheduled departure time.</li>
                <li>Bus passes are non-transferable and must be shown upon request.</li>
                <li>Students must behave appropriately and respect the driver and fellow passengers.</li>
                <li>Any damage to the bus will be the responsibility of the student involved.</li>
                <li>Loud music and disruptive behavior are strictly prohibited.</li>
                <li>Bus routes and schedules are subject to change without prior notice.</li>
                <li>Failure to comply with these rules may result in suspension of bus privileges.</li>
                <li>Keep the bus clean. Dispose of trash in the bins provided.</li>
                <li>In case of emergency, follow the driver's instructions immediately.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
    